{"id": "1439272442114871437", "channel_id": "1439272442114871437", "type": 0, "author_id": "201676421846925312", "author_name": "crescendo09", "author_bot": false, "content": "Do I understand that right, the new season pass premium gives triple daily exp, ergo 1500 EXP. But the bonus EXP from silver prime (15,30,45% etc) doesnt apply because in the description it states (only the strongest effect applies) so that means only the \"200%\" (Triple EXP) of the new premium pass? Or do actually both take effect?", "timestamp": "2025-11-15T15:14:50.589000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1439272442114871437", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Bonus EXP Interaction between new Premium Pass Triple EXP and Silver Prime Bonus EXP", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1439246707098386543", "channel_id": "1439246707098386543", "type": 0, "author_id": "1171539234176389241", "author_name": "theborkerr", "author_bot": false, "content": "In the main story, we first meet Goliath in the new world when the Seafarers try to invade Necrovia.\n\nHowever, the dialogue between Goliath and the Keeper suggests that they met before, which makes it confusing because again, this should be the first time we are meeting him in this world.\n\nI asked other players and they said this was because we've already met Goliath in the story for the 1.5 anniversary raid event.\n\nI wasn't able to read that event story and I'm sure new players will also be unable to read it because it's not archived.\n\nSo now, this leaves us this dialogue in the main story with zero context from the main story itself.\n\nPlease considering editing this dialogue to make it more consistent with the main story.", "timestamp": "2025-11-15T13:32:34.883000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-15T14:53:19.201000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "shocked", "emoji_id": "1400771713498746901", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Feelguilty", "emoji_id": "1400771618174664775", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1439246707538923570", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-11-15-18-39-43-951_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 135996, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1439246707098386543/1439246707538923570/Screenshot_2025-11-15-18-39-43-951_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbccf2&is=69ca7b72&hm=c676e330e95f4199ae5ee184fb31bf05943a66a99baae9b903bbc15200038c44&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1439246707098386543", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Goliath's interaction with the Keeper in Arc 2 Chapter 3 is inconsistent with the main story", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
